{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC02_REG_810.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x23,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "*sigh*"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, what's wrong? It's rare to see you sigh like that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, I've just been thinking...<CR>Oh, I know, can I ask you something?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "How long do you plan on being an apothecary?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Like making medicine? Hmm, I've never thought about that before..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "But I think I'll still be doing it even after I become a grandma."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Okay, I see. Maybe I should've chosen a job like that, too..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "What's the matter all of a sudden? You're acting weird today, Regina."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Hmm... I got a letter from my parents. They told me to come home soon."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "And that means I have to quit my job."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Huh...? You're gonna quit being a prospector...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Well, I'm sure my parents are worried. For a girl to be digging holes..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "They start saying selfish things, like settle down already, or how they want to see grandkids."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "If I had a partner, I'd bring him to meet them, even without being asked."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "S-So Regina, are you going home...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Hmm... That's the hard part.<CR>My parents do have a point."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "And I'm not getting any younger. This isn't a job that a girl can do forever."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "*sigh* Maybe I should've gotten a job I could keep doing into my old age like you, Ayesha..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Regina..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "When I started out as a prospector,<CR>I felt like I had made a crucial<CR>decision, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Looking back, it wasn't that hard of a call to make. My parents supported my decision, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "But when it comes to quitting,<CR>I just can't make up my mind."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x166,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Like, what would I do after I quit, and will everything I've done till now become a waste of time...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x166,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "I start to think deeply about that, which just isn't like me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x166,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "And not just jobs, but maybe everything is harder to stop than it is to start."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I can understand why your parents are worried, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "I just hope everything will work out in a way where you won't be left with any regrets..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "In the end, your life is your own, Regina."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x167,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "My life is my own...<CR>Yup, you're absolutely right."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Whether I keep my job or quit,<CR>I would like to come out of this<CR>with no regrets."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I'm sorry. I got kinda gloomy there for a second..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "But I haven't decided if I'm gonna quit yet."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "If I make my decision,<CR>I'll let you know."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "(If Regina goes back home,<CR>it's gonna get lonely...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "(But it's Regina's life. If that<CR>happens...I have to send her off<CR>with a smile...)"
        }
    ]
}